{"tid":308032,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(埃及神話現代異能漫畫)大祭師伊姆霍特普","createTime":"2017-07-03T21:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T17:04:57.000Z","uid":6327,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f83ab0512164aad1044a7f0a29800f7e8d7b4528","tid":308032,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T21:42:52.000Z","msg":"故事講一個古埃及時代既上位祭師(主角)<br />\n係當時因為「一個錯誤」導致世界往後出現好多偽神而成為大罪人比人封印<br />\n多年後比神解除封印要求執翻自己蘇洲屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">所謂既神冇個好人</span><br />\n成套野既氛圍係頭幾話比較輕鬆...但一入主線就睇到停唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/053101_7f9540ef77dffd0f242f636a86f16628.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F053101_7f9540ef77dffd0f242f636a86f16628.jpg&h=8934508a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後遇上女主角...女主角因為比偽神附身所以唔可以講嘢 一講嘢會著火<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/053626_2910aa2a30cb812f7d79da44653a3c3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F053626_2910aa2a30cb812f7d79da44653a3c3e.jpg&h=5532e224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上說話都唔算重點...重點係呢套野好快就入主線<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/053322_26b1c3032403f0aa853c35d580742768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F053322_26b1c3032403f0aa853c35d580742768.jpg&h=45e851bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想劇透太多....請務必睇到七話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再決定係咪睇落去<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/054110_cd7c958542a0a899130b2fa74793438b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F054110_cd7c958542a0a899130b2fa74793438b.jpg&h=e7060049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/053457_31a7cb155ceda7ed9f3ebe348b17f554.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F053457_31a7cb155ceda7ed9f3ebe348b17f554.jpg&h=327bd861&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca5254ebc208dc55bf936a65fd3f39a46274013a","tid":308032,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d7fdda72d52d3204962e7fee73bd2a95253b36","tid":308032,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:17:46.000Z","msg":"呢套有睇 唔記得睇到邊話<br />\n大概係 岩岩入主線 比個分部長話 唔洗返埃及個話<br />\n<br />\n男主平時d行為好仆街好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427ff5d0d6e28d4c2bbcbb771cc84954cdc73792","tid":308032,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢套有睇 唔記得睇到邊話<br />\n大概係 岩岩入主線 比個分部長話 唔洗返埃及個話<br />\n<br />\n男主平時d行為好仆街好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鳩下鳩下咁但係最靠得住就係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nd配角都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個王子同埋晴天型到爆<br />\n最新果幾集女主爆seed睇到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9fedf36d0599a3092363062087225e3f180fc6d","tid":308032,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dcd8bee6b97d71131f27b99dc054ab9ca4d784e8","tid":308032,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f88473e791b64b3cfed0faef8430bba83b93123","tid":308032,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998652e8770895c3c3bf84bc681f9b2c95e2e427","tid":308032,"uid":23584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"一直有追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但更新得好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419cbf400e158378b297c3bac1fe7d7e1b63dbe2","tid":308032,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T10:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直有追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但更新得好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個月一集算係咁啦"},{"pid":"e51657301101ca87c452f225eded4a9e88b2f2b3","tid":308032,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T10:06:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"293c96ccd5e62a89f0599f862aa53bb2e5263369","tid":308032,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T10:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好睇 仲有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要邊類 中長篇既話 <br />\n我推介：地獄三頭犬的日常<br />\n亦都係有主線...男主因為一d原因導致失去左笑既功能...又係有d奇幻野...女主角有三個人格..中期分翻開做三個人"},{"pid":"8e4c9927eebd115304b1143b59b544a356261705","tid":308032,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:50:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"657147b8a5a6b40ce9bbfe82e2265fa0e5a14286","tid":308032,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e75849923db70af0b514224f6fef9321c1fcac65","tid":308032,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666081b8ac13c83032b9bfe907fa448052258726","tid":308032,"uid":74101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:53:35.000Z","msg":"仲有冇D神話漫畫推介?"},{"pid":"0cc910435c560a3bd828f34dde45d8dbd6f6fe3e","tid":308032,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有冇D神話漫畫推介?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4849a446e2b6915012b62fe35b0468f5f4f884","tid":308032,"uid":16515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:54:33.000Z","msg":"法國神父推介果d我都有睇開"},{"pid":"29f411e2abcaa688910df1b87c063928dafeb57b","tid":308032,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法國神父推介果d我都有睇開</blockquote><br />\n做神父信徒會比佢吸運"},{"pid":"f9b6eaf293dab151ac4ddd99a6759b8fadbf40e2","tid":308032,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:09:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法國神父推介果d我都有睇開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你眼光好姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8922f5518f82b03ef401f93521fac1da77305ef","tid":308032,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy